#: src/0066-better-temporary-lifetimes.md:7
msgid ""
"Temporaries live for the enclosing block when found in a let-binding. This "
"only holds when the reference to the temporary is taken directly. This logic "
"should be extended to extend the cleanup scope of any temporary whose "
"lifetime ends up in the let-binding."
msgstr ""

